--To install:

Go to the section of MongoDB page:

Products --> Community Edition --> Community Server

Download it wihtout installing Compass



--Then in the Hyper command linux of 'vim .bash_profile', press the 'i' key and insert the following:

alias mongod="/c/Program\ files/MongoDB/Server/6.0/bin/mongod.exe"

alias mongos="/c/Program\ Files/MongoDB/Server/6.0/bin/mongos.exe"

--Stop inserting by pressing the 'esc' key and type :wq!


Restart hyper, then put:

mongos --version



Then it should be all done!
